---
const partners = ['OPCO', 'CPF', 'France Travail', '3FPT Sénégal', 'FDFP CI'];
---

<section class="funding" id="financement">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Découvrez nos<br/>options de <em>financement</em></h2>
    <p>OgunLearn est un organisme de formation certifié Qualiopi. Nos formations sont éligibles à plusieurs dispositifs de financement — pour particuliers comme pour entreprises.</p>
    <a href="/financement" class="funding__btn">
      Découvrir les financements
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
    <div class="funding__partners">
      {partners.map((p, i) => (
        <>
          <span>{p}</span>
          {i < partners.length - 1 && <span>·</span>}
        </>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .funding {
    background: var(--coral);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .funding h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.6vw, 60px);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .funding h2 :global(em) { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink); }
  .funding p {
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    opacity: .95;
  }
  .funding__btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px;
    transition: all var(--t-base);
  }
  .funding__btn:hover {
    background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .funding__partners {
    display: flex; gap: 32px;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center;
    margin-top: 56px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: .9;
  }
  .funding__partners span {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
</style>
